transcription.text:

Speaker 2: How can I help you today?

Speaker 1: Yeah, I guess I signed up for an auto renewal

Speaker 2: and I want to cancel that.

Speaker 1: OK, sir.

Speaker 2: I'm happy to help you with this.

Speaker 1: Could you please provide me with the full name and date of birth

Speaker 2: under the prescription?

Speaker 1: It is B-A-R-R-Y, B-E-C-K-E-R. That's

Speaker 2: 10-22-1950.

Speaker 2: I'm looking at your prescription right here.

Speaker 1: It looks like it was written in November

Speaker 2: for the 100 milligram Viagra AGV, a quantity of 25

Speaker 1: each fulfillment.

Speaker 2: Here's the doctor wrote it here with refills every two months.

Speaker 1: So yeah, Mr. Becker, you're not required or obligated

Speaker 2: to get this on a monthly or bimonthly schedule.

Speaker 1: This is by no means a subscription.

Speaker 2: If you want, you can keep this prescription active

Speaker 1: and essentially just pause it.

Speaker 2: And that would allow you to call in and place

Speaker 1: future orders as needed.

Speaker 2: It looks like you have about 10 refills left under the script.

Speaker 1: Yeah, I'd like to do that, call when needed.

Speaker 2: So I'll go ahead and put that pause on the account.

Speaker 1: And you are all set, sir.

Speaker 2: OK, is there any kind of confirmation

Speaker 1: or could you send me something on that?

Speaker 2: Yeah, yeah, I can get you a confirmation on the pause.

Speaker 1: Yeah.

Speaker 2: Let me put that request in with our system.

Speaker 1: And then you are all set.

Speaker 2: You have an email, right?

Speaker 1: Yeah, the email I have on file here is Barry219592005

Speaker 2: at gmail.com.

Speaker 1: Correct.

Speaker 2: Can you send me a little email on that?

Speaker 1: Of course, I'll do that right now.

Speaker 2: Great, thank you so much.

Speaker 1: I appreciate it.

Speaker 2: What's your name?

Speaker 1: My name is Nick.

Speaker 2: Nick, N-I-C-K?

Speaker 1: Yes, sir.

Speaker 2: All right, Nick, I appreciate that.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: Oh, yeah, happy to help.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: You bet.

Speaker 1: Take care.
